{"type": "article", "id": 24674, "title": "一周年节庆啤酒", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-30T07:01:03Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 23, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607124452rRWfbPJ8TX5tiezw.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://taftsalehouse.com/\">Taft’s Ale House </a>是在美国辛辛那提（Cincinnati）成立的一家新的啤酒吧，这是他们一周年的纪念包装。 500ml 的啤酒都装在特质的木盒子里，是当地的一种传统。啤酒颈部有 9 种不一样的旗帜，其中有一款旗帜是用樱桃木片制作的，上面印出了金属色的 logo，都是细微处的简单改变，增加了节日的仪式感。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607124451ZVFER6fqMiXoQLWT.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"1.27881041\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607124451gANV30bGkixfmcqO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.10037175\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071244521rfz7XFwQ6EWKJSv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71933086\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607124452zlDghP1ZfKNcXM0B.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.79182156\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}